    "description": "本課程介紹永續的概念，探討人們在面對全球變化、生態系統惡化及資源限制時，如何為生存和福祉而努力。在本課程中，學生將了解跨領域的永續發展議題，包括人口、生態系統、全球變化、能源、倫理和文化歷史。<br><br>This course introduces the concept of Sustainability and explores how people can do for survival and well-being in the face of global change, ecosystem degradation and resource limitations. In this course, students will be familiarized with cross-disciplinary issues on sustainability, including population, ecosystems, global change, energy, ethics, and cultural history.",
